        "title": "fix(memory): keep QMD background refreshes armed",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- keep QMD background refresh managers armed when startup is configured for interval/embed work even if boot sync is disabled\n- make memory watch ignores relative to configured collection roots so a root named `build`, `dist`, `vendor`, or `.cache` is not ignored wholesale\n- centralize the QMD startup-work predicate and document that `onBoot: false` suppresses only the boot refresh, not interval/embed maintenance startup\n- isolate the deadcode pnpm fallback test from CI-managed `PATH` state\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/gateway/server-startup-memory.test.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.test.ts extensions/memory-core/src/memory/qmd-manager.test.ts test/scripts/check-deadcode-unused-files.test.ts` (13 tooling + 118 gateway + 125 memory-extension tests passed)\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.full-core-support-boundary.config.ts` (3229 passed, 15 skipped)\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxlint extensions/memory-core/src/memory/qmd-manager.ts src/gateway/server-startup-memory.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.test.ts test/scripts/check-deadcode-unused-files.test.ts`\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check extensions/memory-core/src/memory/qmd-manager.test.ts extensions/memory-core/src/memory/qmd-manager.ts src/gateway/server-startup-memory.test.ts src/gateway/server-startup-memory.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.test.ts src/gateway/server-startup-post-attach.ts test/scripts/check-deadcode-unused-files.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `node scripts/check-changed.mjs --dry-run`\n\nBroad `pnpm check:changed` was not run locally because this shell has no `pnpm` or `corepack`; PR CI should cover that full lane before merge.\n",
